## 9) Data Model (MVP)

### `users`
- `id` (uuid, pk)
- `auth_provider` (enum: email, google, apple)
- `email` (uniq), `display_name`, `bio`, `avatar_url`
- `created_at`, `updated_at`
- `location_geohash`, `city`, `state`, `country`
