### `plants`
- `id`, `common_name`, `scientific_name`, `care_light` (enum), `care_water` (enum), `care_notes`

### `listings`
- `id`, `owner_id (fk users)`, `plant_id (fk plants | nullable)`
- `title`, `description`, `transaction_types` (array enum: swap, sale, free)
- `price_cents` (nullable), `is_active` (bool), `quantity` (int)
- `condition` (enum: cutting, seed, juvenile, mature)
- `propagation_notes`
- `photos` (array of urls), `thumbnail_url`
- `geohash`, `city`, `state`, `radius_km`
- `created_at`, `expires_at` (nullable), `updated_at`

### `matches`
- `id`, `listing_id`, `liker_id`, `status` (enum: pending, matched, rejected)
- `created_at`

### `messages`
- `id`, `thread_id`, `sender_id`, `recipient_id`, `body`, `attachments`, `created_at`, `read_at`

### `ratings`
- `id`, `rater_id`, `ratee_id`, `swap_id`, `reliability` (1–5), `health` (1–5), `notes`, `created_at`

### `swaps`
- `id`, `listing_id`, `buyer_id` (nullable for swap), `seller_id`, `type` (swap|sale|free)
- `status` (proposed, agreed, completed, canceled, no_show)
- `scheduled_at` (nullable), `location_hint`, `created_at`

### `reports`
- `id`, `reporter_id`, `reported_user_id` (nullable), `listing_id` (nullable)
- `type` (spam, pest, harassment, counterfeit, other), `notes`, `created_at`, `status`

### `wishlists`
- `id`, `user_id`, `criteria` (JSON: species, rarity, type, distance_km), `created_at`

### `notifications`
- `id`, `user_id`, `type`, `payload(json)`, `delivered_at`, `read_at`

