## 10) Key Flows (Happy Paths)

### A) Onboarding
1. Install → Allow location (coarse) → Sign in (Apple/Google/Email)  
2. Set radius (default 10 mi) → Pick interests (species/tags) → Done

### B) Create a Listing
1. Tap “+ List” → Add photos → Title, type (swap/sell/free), price (optional)
2. Select plant (autocomplete or free text) → condition → notes
3. Confirm geofence area → Publish

### C) Browse & Match
1. Swipe screen: like or pass cards → instant “Match!” when a seller accepts or using “Message Seller” on detail.  
2. Map screen: filter → tap pin → view listing → like/message.

### D) Chat & Schedule
1. In chat, quick replies: “Available today 5–7pm?” “Meet at library?”  
2. Mark as **Agreed** → after meetup, mark **Completed** → trigger ratings.

