## 11) API Surface (MVP, REST examples)

```
POST   /auth/signup
POST   /auth/login
GET    /users/me
PATCH  /users/me

GET    /plants/search?q=monstera
POST   /plants        (admin only for canonical list; free text stored in listings otherwise)

POST   /listings
GET    /listings?lat=..&lng=..&radius_km=..&filters=..&sort=..
GET    /listings/{id}
PATCH  /listings/{id}
DELETE /listings/{id}

POST   /matches/{listingId}/like
POST   /matches/{listingId}/pass
GET    /matches

POST   /threads (or auto-create on message)
POST   /messages
GET    /threads
GET    /messages?thread_id=...

POST   /swaps/{id}/status (agreed | completed | canceled | no_show)
POST   /ratings

POST   /reports
GET    /notifications
```

**Auth:** Bearer JWT.  
**Rate limiting:** per-IP + per-user (e.g., 60 req/min).

