## 12) Trust & Safety
- **Ratings after completion** required to keep the community healthy.
- **Report & Block** at user and listing level.
- **Image moderation** pipeline (NSFW, QR code spam, text filters).
- **Anti‑scam tips** injected in chat (no deposits, meet in public, etc.).
- **Location privacy:** Only show coarse area; never show exact home address.

---

## 13) Content & UX Details
- **Card Layout (Swipe):** Large photo → title → badges (swap/sale/free, cutting/mature) → distance → quick actions (like, save, message).  
- **Map View:** Cluster markers; bottom sheet w/ listing details & CTA.  
- **Filters:** Type (cutting/seed/mature), transaction (swap/sale/free), price range, distance, rarity tags.  
- **Accessibility:** Dynamic type, voiceover labels, sufficient contrast, tap targets ≥ 44pt.

---

## 14) Analytics & KPIs
- D1/D7 retention, sessions/user/day
- Listing creation success rate
- Match rate (likes → chats)
- Swap/sale completion rate
- Report rate (by type)
- Ratings distribution

---

## 15) Monetization (Post‑MVP options)
- **Premium ($/mo):** more photos, featured placement, advanced filters, lower sales fee.  
- **Promoted listings:** pay to boost (local only).  
- **Affiliate links:** optional care kits/supplies (opt‑out in settings).

---

## 16) Roadmap
**MVP (6–8 weeks):** Onboarding, listing, browse (swipe+map), chat, ratings, basic reports, push notifications, admin moderation.  
**Phase 1.5:** Wishlists/alerts, event listings, basic admin dashboard, simple badges.  
**Phase 2:** Payments escrow & seller fees, shipping option (opt‑in), richer reputation (propagation success).

---

## 17) Testing Strategy
- **Unit:** model + util libs (validation, geohash, filters).  
- **Integration:** listing CRUD, search queries, auth flows.  
- **E2E:** Detox/Flutter Driver for onboarding → list → match → chat → complete → rate.  
- **Beta:** TestFlight (iOS) + Internal App Sharing (Android).

---

## 18) Release & Ops
- **CI/CD:** GitHub Actions → build + unit tests → deploy to staging → manual QA → stores.  
- **Feature flags:** Gradual rollout for swipe vs map, premium promo.  
- **Support:** In‑app “Report a problem,” FAQ, community guidelines.

---

## 19) Legal & Compliance
- **ToS/Privacy:** clear about location, photo storage, messaging retention.  
- **COPPA:** 13+ only.  
- **GDPR/CCPA:** data export/delete endpoints.  
- **Trademark:** “PlantMates” availability to be verified; file early if pursuing brand protection.

---

## 20) Acceptance Criteria (MVP)
- A new user can: sign in → set location → view listings in radius → like/pass → view map → message a seller → agree on a swap → mark completed → leave ratings.  
- Listing creation ≤ 60s with at least one photo.  
- Push notifications delivered for matches & messages.  
- Reports flow reaches admin queue.  
- App ships to **iOS and Android** from a single codebase.

---

